            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[# Dictate Anywhere 2.2.14

- Fixed hold-to-record shortcuts that include Space so the trigger key no longer inserts spaces into the active field.
- Improved Custom Vocabulary input to split comma-separated terms and keep long entries removable.
- Added a local transcript history page that keeps the latest 50 final dictations.
]]></description>
